dcterms:description: A dataset containing dense image annotations that connect language and vision, used to curate custom datasets for model training.
dcterms:title: Visual Genome

dcterms:description: A custom dataset created from the Visual Genome dataset containing 3400 images with balanced positive and negative labels for detecting buses or trains.
dcterms:title: Baseline Dataset

dcterms:description: A custom dataset created from the Visual Genome dataset containing 3400 images that are label-balanced but with completely mislabeled positive classes.
dcterms:title: Mislabeled Dataset
